title: Community.720p.1080p.WEB-DL.DD5.1.H.264
description:
Details:

-  This is a 1080p series pack - where available. S01-03 were only available in 720p.

- This is a compilation of various scene releases. The first couple of seasons were only available in 720p; however, S04 and S05 are at 1080p. ENG subtitles are included when available. 

-  The only quirk is that the S04 episodes (untouched) have a metadata title of "Community.S02E19.720p.HDTV.X264.DIMENSION.mkv 17713"; the file names ARE correct, though.
